It's none of your business.

278
00:13:58,166 --> 00:14:01,166
[KAIRI] Come on, don't push me
away. I'm just trying to help.

279
00:14:01,250 --> 00:14:02,958
[MOMO]
I have to find out the truth.

280
00:14:03,041 --> 00:14:05,083
