281
00:14:05,166 --> 00:14:06,750
[gasps]

282
00:14:06,833 --> 00:14:09,208
[KAIRI grunts, groans]

283
00:14:09,291 --> 00:14:10,250
[KAIRI]
Huh?

284
00:14:17,833 --> 00:14:21,083
[KAIRI] Whoa. That's Toji
and Sae, isn't it?

285
00:14:21,166 --> 00:14:24,250
This is crazy! I can't believe
we just caught them cheating!

286
00:14:28,458 --> 00:14:29,625
Momo?

287
00:14:41,708 --> 00:14:42,666
