Sae behind your back.

291
00:14:48,291 --> 00:14:49,583
I told you not to trust him.

292
00:14:49,666 --> 00:14:51,875
I really think that
guy's a sex fiend.

293
00:14:51,958 --> 00:14:53,916
So... How about you
dump that creep

294
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,250
and go out to dinner
with me tonight?

295
00:14:55,333 --> 00:14:56,333
[BOTH grunt]

296
00:14:56,416 --> 00:14:57,958
--[MOMO grunting]
--[KAIRI groaning]

297
00:14:58,041 --> 00:14:59,416
Ow, that hurts!

298
00:14:59,500 --> 00:15:01,666
Geez, Momo, I'm not the one
you should be beating up!

299
00:15:01,750 --> 00:15:05,208
Tell me you love me!
Please, tell me you love me!

300
00:15:05,291 --> 00:15:06,416
Uh?

301
00:15:06,500 --> 00:15:11,458
[MOMO sobs]

302
00:15:11,541 --> 00:15:14,833
Why was he kissing another girl
and why did it have to be Sae?!

303
00:15:14,916 --> 00:15:17,708
