and then cheat on me?

305
00:15:21,291 --> 00:15:27,250
[MOMO cries]

306
00:15:34,416 --> 00:15:36,583
[MOMO]
I'm sorry.

307
00:15:36,666 --> 00:15:38,875
I'm sorry that I hit you.

308
00:15:42,333 --> 00:15:45,000
--[KAIRI groans]
--You never give up, do you?!

309
00:15:45,083 --> 00:15:48,250
Lay off the face! You're just so
cute when you cry like that.

310
00:15:48,333 --> 00:15:49,500
Sorry.

311
00:15:49,583 --> 00:15:51,000
[MOMO] You get more and
more stupid by the hour!

312
00:15:51,083 --> 00:15:53,458
[KAIRI] Ha-ha. Anyway, I guess
the playing field is level

313
00:15:53,541 --> 00:15:55,583
