It was never intended for you!

318
00:16:03,875 --> 00:16:06,791
Hold on... I think I get it now.

319
00:16:06,875 --> 00:16:08,166
The kiss.

320
00:16:08,250 --> 00:16:09,208
[KAIRI groans]

321
