herself on him.

322
00:16:10,833 --> 00:16:13,083
Toji didn't want to kiss her
but she wouldn't let go of him.

323
00:16:13,166 --> 00:16:15,375
It may have even been
a surprise attack.

324
00:16:15,458 --> 00:16:17,166
Are you sure you're not
just telling yourself

325
