around here.

327
00:16:20,083 --> 00:16:23,250
I know that's what happened
because Toji isn't like that!

328
00:16:23,333 --> 00:16:24,833
Listen...

329
00:16:24,916 --> 00:16:26,958
The portions of a man's brain
that control rational thinking

330
00:16:27,041 --> 00:16:28,375
