an attractive female.

332
00:16:30,250 --> 00:16:32,791
Your Toji is no different
than any other man.

333
00:16:32,875 --> 00:16:33,958
It's a law of nature.

334
00:16:34,041 --> 00:16:35,208
[MOMO growls]

335
00:16:35,291 --> 00:16:36,750
--[KAIRI yelping]
--[MOMO] Do you even hear

336
00:16:36,833 --> 00:16:38,750
