out of your mouth?

337
00:16:44,291 --> 00:16:46,250
[MOMO]
I hope I'm right.

338
00:16:50,166 --> 00:16:53,333
[GIRL E] Is it just me or do
they look like they're a couple?

339
00:16:53,416 --> 00:16:54,958
Yeah, you're right.
They sure do.

340
00:16:55,041 --> 00:16:57,291
And I was hoping Toji would
ask me to go out with him.

341
00:16:57,375 --> 00:17:00,208
[MOMO] You'd never get
a chance 'cause Toji's with me!

342
00:17:00,291 --> 00:17:02,208
Sae thinks she's so clever.

343
00:17:02,291 --> 00:17:04,375
Does she really think
I won't say anything?

344
00:17:04,458 --> 00:17:07,666
And doesn't Toji feel the least
built guilty for what he did?

345
00:17:07,750 --> 00:17:09,833
He seems to be acting
so cool about it.

346
00:17:10,875 --> 00:17:12,125
[MOMO]
Ugh...

347
00:17:12,208 --> 00:17:14,000
I should've never kept
our relationship a secret.

348
00:17:18,958 --> 00:17:20,916
That's it! You're doing
an awesome job!

349
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:24,833
Just act nonchalant like you're
totally fine with what happened.

350
00:17:24,916 --> 00:17:26,250
[MOMO]
She knows.

351
00:17:28,250 --> 00:17:29,458
[MOMO]
It's so obvious!

352
00:17:29,541 --> 00:17:32,208
It's written all over her face.

353
00:17:32,291 --> 00:17:36,000
I see how it is. She has
her sights set on Toji now.

354
00:17:39,041 --> 00:17:41,541
Geez, cool down.
You're starting to scare me.

355
00:17:41,625 --> 00:17:43,916
When you're angry, I can see
that vein pop out of your neck.

356
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:46,250
You know about
me and Toji, don't you?

357
00:17:46,333 --> 00:17:47,333
[SAE]
Uh?

358
00:17:47,416 --> 00:17:49,125
Toji and I are in love
with each other.

359
00:17:49,208 --> 00:17:52,166
And it's not some immature
playground love, it's real.

360
00:17:52,250 --> 00:17:55,125
I want you to stay away from him
from now on, do you hear me?

361
00:17:55,208 --> 00:17:56,458
I can't do that.

362
00:17:56,541 --> 00:17:59,083
Toji and I have been way
into each other lately...

363
00:17:59,166 --> 00:18:01,333
Just earlier today, he
kissed me for like a minute

364
00:18:01,416 --> 00:18:02,750
in the school's garden.

365
00:18:02,833 --> 00:18:05,208
Yeah, I know... I was there...

366
00:18:05,291 --> 00:18:06,458
But from what I saw,

367
00:18:06,541 --> 00:18:08,083
it looked more like you
forced yourself on him.

368
00:18:08,166 --> 00:18:09,541
Isn't that the truth, Sae?

369
00:18:09,625 --> 00:18:10,875
[SAE gasps]

370
00:18:10,958 --> 00:18:14,166
[MOMO]
That got her.

371
00:18:14,250 --> 00:18:17,083
[SAE chuckles]

372
00:18:17,166 --> 00:18:19,000
Oh... You poor thing...

373
00:18:19,083 --> 00:18:20,708
I guess Toji really
wanted to find out

374
00:18:20,791 --> 00:18:23,458
what it was like to
kiss someone like you.

375
00:18:23,541 --> 00:18:25,500
Although, I did
find it a bit weird

376
00:18:25,583 --> 00:18:27,250
that recently he'd been
paying more attention

377
00:18:27,333 --> 00:18:29,291
to you than normal.

378
00:18:29,375 --> 00:18:30,750
You told Kairi the other day

379
00:18:30,833 --> 00:18:33,458
that you'd been in love with
Toji since junior high.

380
00:18:33,541 --> 00:18:35,125
Well, sorry to break
the news to ya,

381
00:18:35,208 --> 00:18:37,291
but Toji and I were
making out at the time.

382
00:18:39,250 --> 00:18:41,125
And for him to tell you
that he's in love with you

383
00:18:41,208 --> 00:18:43,041
