Just say the L word

386
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,750
and she'll do whatever you want.

387
00:18:48,833 --> 00:18:50,375
Sorry about the confusion...

388
00:18:50,458 --> 00:18:53,375
When he comes over later, I'll
tell him all about it, 'kay?

389
00:18:54,666 --> 00:18:56,333
[MOMO gasps]

390
00:18:56,416 --> 00:19:02,833
[STUDENTS chatter]

391
00:19:02,916 --> 00:19:05,625
[SAE] Just say the L word
and she'll do whatever you want.

392
00:19:07,958 --> 00:19:10,250
[MOMO]
No, I don't believe it.

393
00:19:16,208 --> 00:19:19,166
After school I want you to
meet me out by the pool, okay?

394
00:19:19,250 --> 00:19:20,666
