Well, we'll just see

396
00:19:24,500 --> 00:19:26,625
if Mr. Tojigamori
makes that meeting.

397
00:19:26,708 --> 00:19:28,750
[bell chiming]

398
00:19:28,833 --> 00:19:30,791
Hey, Toji!

399
00:19:30,875 --> 00:19:34,208
Momo wants to meet you in the
cafeteria instead of the pool.

400
00:19:34,291 --> 00:19:36,666
She said she'd rather
not go out in the sun.

401
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:38,583
Yeah. That's cool.

402
00:19:38,666 --> 00:19:40,000
See you later.

403
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:48,500
