the hallway 30 minutes ago. Uh?

405
00:19:55,666 --> 00:19:56,875
[KAIRI]
Guess who?

406
00:19:56,958 --> 00:19:58,041
Toji!

407
00:19:59,833 --> 00:20:00,916
[MOMO groans]

408
00:20:09,250 --> 00:20:10,541
[KAIRI]
He's pretty late.

409
00:20:10,625 --> 00:20:12,541
Are you sure he told you
to meet him here?

410
00:20:12,625 --> 00:20:13,625
[MOMO]
Yes.

411
00:20:13,708 --> 00:20:15,625
Though I'm not so sure
why you're here.

412
00:20:15,708 --> 00:20:17,000
I wanted to know how
you were doing,

413
00:20:17,083 --> 00:20:18,375
and since you're
on the swim team,

414
00:20:18,458 --> 00:20:20,750
