to worry. So I'll stay.

418
00:20:28,125 --> 00:20:29,666
This is getting ridiculous.

419
00:20:29,750 --> 00:20:30,916
Why don't you
go check his locker

420
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:32,916
and see if he's even still here?

421
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:35,291
