to meet him here

422
00:20:35,375 --> 00:20:38,250
and that's what I'm gonna do.
He'll be here any minute.

423
00:20:45,250 --> 00:20:46,708
[KAIRI]
Look, Momo.

424
00:20:46,791 --> 00:20:50,083
I'm not trying to be funny.
Drop Toji and go out with me.

425
00:20:54,333 --> 00:20:55,916
