431
00:21:06,166 --> 00:21:09,375
So, would you like me even if
I were still in love with Toji?

432
00:21:09,458 --> 00:21:12,291
Uh! Time out! Forget
I said anything! I was...

433
00:21:12,375 --> 00:21:14,500
Sorry. No backing
out now! You're stuck!

434
00:21:14,583 --> 00:21:18,000
What? Don't tell me
Momo never showed up?

435
00:21:18,083 --> 00:21:19,958
I figured you two would
have hashed everything out

436
00:21:20,041 --> 00:21:22,958
by now, so I dropped
by to see if... [gasps]

437
00:21:23,041 --> 00:21:24,833
I hope she's not...

438
00:21:28,416 --> 00:21:29,583
[BOTH gasp]

439
00:21:32,541 --> 00:21:34,125
What's Kairi doing here?

440
00:21:34,208 --> 00:21:35,500
Makes sense.

441
00:21:35,583 --> 00:21:38,041
What do you mean "makes sense"?
You know something?

442
00:21:38,125 --> 00:21:40,041
[SAE] Momo was just saying
today how much more fun

443
00:21:40,125 --> 00:21:42,250
