about you being boring.

445
00:21:44,458 --> 00:21:46,916
I thought she was kidding,
but I guess not.

446
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:48,375
Toji, wait!

447
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:51,375
[SAE chuckles]

448
00:21:51,458 --> 00:21:52,333
[TOJI grunts]

449
00:21:52,416 --> 00:21:54,000
Hi!

450
00:21:54,083 --> 00:21:55,000
[MOMO gasps]

451
00:21:55,083 --> 00:21:56,375
Toji!

452
00:21:56,458 --> 00:21:57,416
[KAIRI gasps]

453
00:21:58,666 --> 00:22:00,458
[MOMO]
Wait a minute! Hold on!

454
00:22:00,541 --> 00:22:03,041
