456
00:22:09,958 --> 00:22:11,500
Why did he bring me here?

457
00:22:15,500 --> 00:22:17,125
[MOMO]
What's this all about?

458
00:22:17,208 --> 00:22:18,333
[SAE]
He must have assumed

459
00:22:18,416 --> 00:22:20,583
that getting a kiss
from you would be easy.

460
00:22:20,666 --> 00:22:21,625
[MOMO gasps]

461
00:22:25,375 --> 00:22:26,416
[MOMO]
No!

462
00:22:32,458 --> 00:22:33,750
[MOMO]
Toji...

463
00:24:07,333 --> 00:24:08,791
[SAE]
What should I do now?

464
00:24:08,875 --> 00:24:10,250
Momo's really mad at me,

465
00:24:10,333 --> 00:24:12,833
and word's gotten out around
school that I kissed Toji.

466
00:24:12,916 --> 00:24:15,958
But his lips were softer than
I could have ever imagined.

467
00:24:16,041 --> 00:24:17,708
I'm sure I'll figure
something out...

468
00:24:17,791 --> 00:24:19,041
Next time on Peach Girl:

469
00:24:19,125 --> 00:24:21,500
"How Far Will You Go,
Super Sae?"

